    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; 5 Engine Service Manual - Fuel System - Installation - Horizontal Fuel
        Conditioning Module (HFCM)
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="m7.5" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Horizontal Fuel Conditioning Module (HFCM)</title>
        <figure id="f3001302.5" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj11/j11059.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="392px" box="no"/>
            <caption>HFCM (chassis mounted)</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel supply port to engine</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel return port from engine</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel return port to tank</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel supply port to HFCM</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Electric fuel pump connection</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">WIF electrical connection</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Water drain plug</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Mounting grommet (3)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Fuel heater electrical connection</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Primary filter element cap</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">CityStar&#8482; - Install HFCM to chassis rail. Thread three M8 mounting nuts onto mounting
                M8 x 40 bolts and tighten to
                <hotlnk document="eges390_208.xml" xrefid="E30013B" appearance="hottext">special torque
                    <xref refid="E30013B"/>
                </hotlnk>
                .
            </para>
            <para>Stripped chassis - Install HFCM to transmission housing mounting bracket. Thread three M8 mounting
                nuts onto M8 x 40 mounting bolts and tighten to
                <hotlnk document="eges390_208.xml" xrefid="E30013B" appearance="hottext">special torque
                    <xref refid="E30013B"/>
                </hotlnk>
                .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install new retaining clips onto fuel hoses.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install fuel hoses onto HFCM cover plate.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect the WIF, fuel heater, and fuel pump electrical connectors.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Close water drain plug.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
